<h2>Include additional data</h2>

<p>The <%= link_to( 'MNIS API', 'https://data.parliament.uk/membersdataplatform/memberquery.aspx' ) %> restricts the number of additional datasets included to a <%= link_to( 'maximum of three', 'https://data.parliament.uk/membersdataplatform/memberquery.aspx#outputs' ) %>.</p>

<p>Including additional data for Member records may return multiple nested records. A CSV of the result set may include additional columns.</p>

